# CLAUDE.md

This file provides guidance to Claude Code (claude.ai/code) when working with code in this repository.

> **Maintenance:** Keep this file under **40,000 characters**. Before saving, run `wc -c CLAUDE.md`. If at/over the limit, compress § Recent Feature Updates first (one-line entries, drop paragraphs) and prune any quick-ref already externalised to `.docs/common-issues/`.

## Project Overview

{{PRODUCT_NAME}} Android is a banking application for Small and Medium Business (SMB) customers. The app supports two main business domains:
- **Lending**: Loan applications, disbursement, repayment management
- **Funding**: Account management, transfers, multi-account features

Built with modern Android development practices using Jetpack Compose, Hilt, and Clean Architecture.

